&lt;h2 id=&quot;record-a-stunt&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#record-a-stunt&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: record-a-stunt&quot;&gt;Record a Stunt&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
